strings:
<voice_0x0100111E><se_def>*: Well, well, Cash.
So you finally caught up!
<voice_0x0100111F><se_def>*: Carrie's already gone on ahead, though.
<voice_0x01001120><se_def>*: I'm afraid I couldn't keep up with her...

<voice_0x01001121><se_high>*: There you are at last, Cash!
I'm afraid you're too late, though.
<voice_0x01001122><se_high>*: Carrie came by here ages ago now.

<voice_0x0100112E><se_high>*: I'd stop wasting my time and get going
if I were you.
<voice_0x01001124><se_def>*: Huh. I had no idea the monsters in here were so strong.
<voice_0x01001125><se_def>*: Carrie went on ahead and left me behind when I got injured. She's in terrible danger...

<voice_0x01001126><se_def>*: If you find her and she's in trouble,
just forget about the trial.
Don't let the monsters harm her...

<voice_0x01001127><se_def>Cash: This is probably just some kind of trick.
She did put sleeping powder in our food,
after all.
<voice_0x01001128><se_def>Cash: I can't believe she'd leave someone injured like that, though. She must be in a real panic...

<voice_0x01001129><se_def>*: Well, well, Carrie.
So you finally caught up!
<voice_0x0100112A><se_def>*: Cash has already gone on ahead, though.
<voice_0x0100112B><se_def>*: I'm afraid I couldn't keep up with him...

<voice_0x0100112C><se_high>*: There you are, Carrie!
I'm afraid you're too late, though.
<voice_0x0100112D><se_high>*: Cash came by here ages ago.

<voice_0x0100112E><se_high>*: I'd stop wasting my time and get going
if I were you.
<voice_0x01001124><se_def>*: Huh. I had no idea the monsters in here were so strong.
<voice_0x0100112F><se_def>*: Cash went on ahead and left me behind when I got injured. He's in terrible danger...

<voice_0x01001130><se_def>*: If you find him and he's in trouble,
just forget about the trial.
Don't let the monsters harm him...

<voice_0x01001131><se_high>Carrie: Hm, I don't know.
After what he did with the sleeping powder...
Maybe this is just another dumb trick.
<voice_0x01001132><se_high>Carrie: Anyway, it serves him right if he gets himself into trouble, leaving an injured man behind like that! That's, like, SO low!
